Subject: drm/xe: clean up fault injection usage
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: ccbfd2df3018e2694f750abe5e93b647a4eef5b1
